sc-Box2D is a simple wrapper for the Box2D physics engine intended for use with the Cinder framework.
Wraps Box2D version 2.2.1

Includes:
Sandbox for easier world creation
Conversion methods from physics to screen coords within sandbox

Goals:
Simplify initial Box2d world setup and coordinate conversion
Simplify Box2d body creation
Minimize additional classes/interfaces to learn beyond Box2d

Box2D is copyright Erin Catto, the source (and license) of which are in src/Box2D